race.comment: MAHJING (7) has been thereabouts without winning but won't get a better chance to break through. Wound up strongly last time and looks tough to beat this line-up. LOU LOU'S CHOICE (8) looks the main threat. Placed over the border two back then midfield last time. Races on speed and worth noting did win only try at course and distance. Should run well. BRONCO REVOLUTION (2) has sound recent form. Has placed last couple in tougher company and despite the wide gate expected to take catching. GOT OUT THE FENCE (1) resumes in a thin race. Has won first up in the past and 4kg claim used to good effect. WAKITI BULL (5) resumes from a long spell and is fitter for a recent trial win. Aided by the claim and looks a win chance fresh.
